      • PieChartClass

        public PieChartClass(DataTable currentDataTable,
                     java.lang.String chartNumColName,
                     java.lang.String chartTextColName,
                     java.lang.String currentDatasetName)
        Construct a pie chart with selected numeric column and text column of a selected DataTable.

        The title of the line chart will be "Pie Chart of " plus the name of selected DataTable.

        Parameters:
        currentDataTable - the selected DataTable
        chartNumColName - name of the selected DataColumn for numeric column
        chartTextColName - name of the selected DataColumn for text column
        currentDatasetName - name of the selected DataTable

        The PieChartClass implements the readExternal method to restore its contents by calling the readObject method of ObjectOutput for strings and numbers.
